@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_isabzr(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = v1
    v0 = ((tmp * (v2 + 0.75 + v0 + 0.05)) - tmp)
    v2 = (0.77 / v2)
    v2 = ((wp.abs(v2 + 0.24) * 0.95) * ((v1 + 0.05 - v2 + 0.42) - 0.55))
    data[tid] = v0
